Author: DuyAnhZeroBank
Title: 🔥[ANN][WHITELIST] Zerobank — Your Local Currency🔥
Body: Compare to the commonly used ERC 20 standard, ERC223 is backwards compatible with it meaning every software that supports ERC20 will also supports ERC223. The biggest change is that ERC223 no longer allow token to be transferred to a contract that does not allow token to be withdrawn meaning if someone send their token into such contract that has not allowed anyone to use it, the token will simply be locked and can never leave that contract. It can also save transaction fees in terms of gas.

Title: 🔥[ANN][WHITELIST] Zerobank — Your Local Currency🔥
Body: In traditional money transfer system, there are many processes, which will cost a great deal of money, from 6 to 10% of the amount transferes. THose cost could be cash handling, transfer cost, exchange rate differ between countries, double exchange rate for uncommon currency and so on. ZeroBank aims to eliminate most of that by just having commission fee, intended to be about 2%.

Author: DuyAnhZeroBank
Title: 🔥[ANN][WHITELIST] Zerobank — Your Local Currency🔥
Body: Well, first ZeroBank isn't a bank as the aim is to eliminate the need for centralised organization. If you don't understand the role of shops or taxi drivers, when someone go to their shops or on their taxis, they can receive the money and send somewhere else or give the customers the afore-agreed money via ZeroBank's system. Author: DuyAnhZeroBank
Title: 🔥[ANN][WHITELIST] Zerobank — Your Local Currency🔥
Body: Compare to the ERC 20 standard, ERC223 is backwards compatible with it meaning every software that supports ERC20 will also supports ERC223. The biggest change is that ERC223 no longer allow token to be transferred to a contract that does not allow token to be withdrawn meaning if someone send their token into a contract that has not allowed anyone to use it, the token will simply be locked and can never leave that contract. It can save transaction fees in terms of gas. Moreover, in recent time, bugs of ERC-20 were being exploited, leading to the suspension of trading activities with the ERC-20 tokens, so ERC-223 is safer.

Author: DuyAnhZeroBank
Title: 🔥[ANN][WHITELIST] Zerobank — Your Local Currency🔥
Body: In the traditional centralized model, there are money transfering organizations, banks between cash senders and receivers, which make it time-consuming and expensive. In ZeroBank decentralized model however, ZeroBank provides the app, platform, on which agents can send their token as a kind of settlement instrument, which help reduce third parties involve in the process, thereby lowering the cost. It is like the model of Uber, as ZeroBank is also based on sharing economy. For more information on how the system works, please visit: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFYw7MGuw7o&t=53s or our website at: zerobank.cash.
